	   <tr><td colspan=2>Just to be clear, Aura of Battle is +2regen all the time (standing or sitting) and +21ATK. This is not a trivial change in attack, and the regen is always great to have. More AC on this would be nice, but rangers in particular should kill for this - especially once they have their epics.<br><br>Get a clue if you think this is lame, or better yet, just don't roll on it when we both have the chance - I'll take it!<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
